{"entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"bngul","text":"乡土中国——费孝通","type":"header-one","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"14ddl","text":"","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9pspv","text":"","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7kcfn","text":"乡土本色","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"d0d67","text":"学而时习之，不亦说乎。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"e1g4k","text":"学：接触新事物。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"73ori","text":"习：陶练，反复接触。如：习以为常。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"al7oh","text":"不亦说乎：习而熟练之后的亲密感。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"604ub","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9a8s","text":"生于斯，长于斯，死于斯。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2ojb3","text":"face to face group。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7l84i","text":"熟人社会，不同社区（A镇B镇）之间的交流少。鸡犬相闻民至老死不相往来。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"daqkn","text":"但在村子里，通过一个人的脚步声判断来者何人。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9l80m","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cv3je","text":"和美国的一家人成立一个单位不同，中国的农村多事群而居之。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7j52c","text":"当农村的人口繁衍而达到饱和点之后，人口的迁徙随之发生。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"1fm7d","text":"我所出生的地方即从别处迁徙而来。经以时日，形成村落。","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ca0g3","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"75rt8","text":"土地是农村的根本。农民赖土地而生存繁衍。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"c128","text":"随着城市的兴起和扩张，农村被掏空在即。土也成为需要被掩饰的气息。衣锦还乡失去了往日的市场。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"b6b5d","text":"从熟人社会到陌生人社会。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9j0vp","text":"","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"e8qcg","text":"社会学将社会分为两种：","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"bnc0g","text":"为了完成一件任务而结合的社会；——法理社会","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"48sv0","text":"在一起生长而发生的社会。——礼俗社会。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3lrav","text":"","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9gkbh","text":"现代社会是一个陌生人的社会，讲究口述无凭、立字为据。法律应运而生。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"bv417","text":"","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"df6pc","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"1mjlp","text":"文字下乡","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4q8v1","text":"农村人愚？是指智力不如人，还是知识不如人？","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6ojt1","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6iqgv","text":"语言只能在一个社群所有相同经验的一层上发生。群体愈大，包括的人的所有经验愈繁杂，发生语言的一层共同基础也必然愈有限，于是语言也愈趋于简单化。（P.12）","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4ao5t","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2i83j","text":"行话。特殊语言。inner-group language。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"5naes","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"18b7d","text":"\"特殊语言“ 常是特别有效，因为他可以摆脱字句的固定意义。语言像是个社会定下的筛子，如果我们有一种情意和这筛子的个子不同就漏不下去。我想大家必然有过”无言胜似有言“的经验。其实这个筛子虽则帮助了任何人间的了解，而同时也使人和人间的情意公式化了，使每一个人、每一刻的实际情意都走了一点样。我们永远在削足适履，使感觉敏锐的人怨恨语言的束缚。李常吉要在这束缚中去求比较切近的表达，难怪他要呕心沥血了。（P.13）","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2o5qe","text":"","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"8jhun","text":"再论文字下乡","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3f7hj","text":"乡村没有文字的解释：","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"bhjf1","text":"1、任何人的交流通过口头即可完成。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4qcrk","text":"2、乡村生活是定型的。在定型的生活中长大的有着深入生理基础的习惯帮助我们“日出而作日落而息”的生活节奏。“不知老之将至”既是描写“忘时”的生活。秦亡汉兴，没有关系。乡土社会中不怕忘，而且忘得舒服。只是在轶出于生活常轨的事，当我害怕忘记时，方在指头上打一个结。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"a30km","text":"指头上的结是文字的原始形式，目的就是用外在的象征，利用联想的作用，帮助人的记忆。在一个常常变动的环境中，我们感觉到自己记忆力不够时，方需要这些外在的象征。从语言到文字，也就是从用声音来说词，变到用绳打结，用刀刻图，用笔记字，是出于我们的生活从定型到不定型的过程。在都市中生活，一天到晚接触着陌生面孔的人才需要在袋里藏着本姓名录、通讯簿。在乡土社会中黏着像片的身份证，是毫无意义的。在一个村子里可以以偶一打以上的“王大哥”，绝不会因之认错了人。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"dmpcn","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9bcio","text":"差等。平等。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":6,"style":"BOLD"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"f9sal","text":"人伦，伦，由自己推出去的和自己发生社会关系的那一群人里所发生的一轮轮波纹的差序。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"e1jd4","text":"伦重在分别，在礼记祭祀里有十伦：鬼神、君臣、父子、贵贱、亲疏、爵赏、夫妇、政事、长幼、上下，都是指差等。伦即有差等的次序。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"el65h","text":"","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2k05m","text":"","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"oj2s","text":"系维着私人的道德","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ekl40","text":"一个差序格局的社会，是由无数私人关系搭成的网络。这网络的每一个结附着一种道德要素，因之，传统的道德里不另找出一个笼统性的道德观念来，所有的价值标准也不能超脱于差序的人伦而存在了。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cd73g","text":"中国的道德和法律，都因之得看所施的对象和“自己”的关系而加以程度上的伸缩。····这在差序社会里可以不觉得矛盾；因为在这种社会中，一切普遍的标准并不发生作用，一定要问清了，对象是谁，和自己是什么关系，才能决定拿出什么标准来。","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"1gdo0","text":"","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ob4s","text":"","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"1o3c","text":"","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"c1ol8","text":"家族","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"mfpj","text":"","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"46d97","text":"","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4n5de","text":"","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"5fgsa","text":"","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ekou0","text":"","type":"blockquote","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRange